                    "text": "```ts\n// wagmi onError shape\nonError: (err) => handleWalletError(err, {\n  setStatus: setTxStatus,\n  setErrorMessage: setError,\n  toast,\n  customErrors: { HashMismatch: 'Proof did not match.' },\n})\n\n// catch block shape\ntry {\n  await writeAsync(args)\n} catch (err) {\n  handleWalletError(err, { setStatus, setErrorMessage, toast })\n}\n```"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
